<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Welcome to Easy Vape</title>
</head>
<body style="font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px;">
    <div style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%); padding: 30px; text-align: center; border-radius: 10px 10px 0 0;">
        <h1 style="color: white; margin: 0; font-size: 28px;">Easy Vape</h1>
    </div>
    
    <div style="background: #ffffff; padding: 40px 30px; border: 1px solid #e0e0e0; border-top: none;">
        <h2 style="color: #333; margin-top: 0;">Welcome to Easy Vape! 🎉</h2>
        
        <p>Hi {{ user.firstName }},</p>
        
        <p>Your email has been verified and your account is now active. Welcome to the Easy Vape family!</p>
        
        <p>Here's what you can do now:</p>
        
        <ul style="color: #555;">
            <li>Browse our wide selection of premium vape products</li>
            <li>Save your favorite items to your wishlist</li>
            <li>Track your orders in real-time</li>
            <li>Get exclusive deals and discounts</li>
        </ul>
        
        <div style="text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
            <a href="{{ url('storefront_index') }}" 
               style="display: inline-block; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%); color: white; text-decoration: none; padding: 15px 40px; border-radius: 5px; font-weight: bold; font-size: 16px;">
                Start Shopping
            </a>
        </div>
        
        <hr style="border: none; border-top: 1px solid #eee; margin: 30px 0;">
        
        <p style="color: #666; font-size: 14px;">
            <strong>Need help?</strong> Our customer support team is here for you. Just reply to this email or contact us through our website.
        </p>
    </div>
    
    <div style="text-align: center; padding: 20px; color: #999; font-size: 12px;">
        <p style="margin: 0;">&copy; {{ "now"|date("Y") }} Easy Vape. All rights reserved.</p>
        <p style="margin: 5px 0 0;">You're receiving this because you signed up at Easy Vape.</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
